786
00:35:20,640 --> 00:35:21,814
You promised.

787
00:35:21,815 --> 00:35:22,902
Just greasing the
wheels, Maggie.

788
00:35:22,903 --> 00:35:23,990
Leonard was hugely
helpful today.

789
00:35:23,991 --> 00:35:26,340
Got our EMR back
